  <para>The focus in these sections of the book will be alternative approaches
  for routing of runoff through the available catchment storage. Included in
  this discussion will be the assumptions and conceptualisations necessary for
  implementation of the alternative approaches. While numerical approaches
  will be mentioned, the intention is that reference to published approaches
  will be the main method of discussion of numerical approaches.</para>

